## ğŸš€ Features

* ğŸ” **Search Recipes** by dish name
* ğŸ“· Displays **dish image**
* ğŸ·ï¸ Shows the **category** (e.g., Dessert, Breakfast, etc.)
* ğŸ“– Provides **step-by-step instructions**
* âŒ Handles errors (no recipe found or empty search input)
* ğŸ¨ Responsive design with glassmorphism
* ğŸ“± Mobile-friendly UI

